It’s been in the works for quite some time now and it’s finally here and ready for the official ig announcement. #insightstudios #chicagosfavoritetattooshop has just opened @insightoceanside making that #oceansidesfavoritetattooshop in lovely #Oceanside #California . Never in my wildest dreams would I have ever imagined that #gowestyoungman would ever be applicable to my life but #hereweare . What exactly does this mean? It means that all the #shenanigans brought to you from #1062 will now be #commonplace at #423 . It’s been a ton of work and it’s still #evolving but I’m hoping all the great times and great memories that happened in Chicago with all our awesome clientele will only be enriched out in #SoCal at my new #homeawayfromhome .
